Package net.hypixel.skyblock.blocks

Holds everything related to Block for HypixelSkyBlockMod.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ModCraftingTable  
    TimeSaver
    When this block exists in the world, the world will remain at the indicated time.
    Extended by TimeSaver.DaySaver and TimeSaver.NightSaver.
    If both of these blocks exist in the world, both blocks have no effect.
    TimeSaver.DaySaver
    While this block exists in the world, the world will remain at the indicated day time.
    TimeSaver.NightSaver
    While this block exists in the world, the world will remain at the indicated night time.
